flowchart TD
    %% Self-Improving KB Loop — ship to extract to triage to promote

    SESSION_END["context-session END<br/>Extract candidates to<br/>session-extracts.md"]:::triage
    HARNESS["harness-verify / -maintain<br/>Log failures to<br/>observability-log.md"]:::triage

    HARNESS --> VERDICT{harness-verify verdict?}:::decision
    VERDICT -->|Pass| SYNC["Post-Ship Sync<br/>(context-memory sweep)"]:::sync
    VERDICT -->|Fail| HARNESS

    SYNC -->|sweep each file in INDEX.md| FILES{Update or<br/>untouched?}:::decision
    FILES -->|Update| MEM_UPD["Directly update memory files<br/>(PKB, constitution, architecture, etc.)"]:::sync
    FILES -->|Untouched| SWEEP_REC["Append sweep record to<br/>session-extracts.md"]:::sync

    MEM_UPD --> SWEEP_REC
    SWEEP_REC --> TRIAGE["Extraction Triage<br/>(context-memory)"]:::triage
    SESSION_END --> TRIAGE
    HARNESS --> TRIAGE

    TRIAGE --> DECIDE{Triage Action?}:::decision
    DECIDE -->|Promote Heuristic| HEUR["learned-heuristics.md"]:::promote
    DECIDE -->|Promote Fact/Pattern| PKB["project-knowledge-base.md<br/>or docs/architecture.md"]:::promote
    DECIDE -->|Promote Normative Rule| CONST["constitution.md<br/>(CC-* with user approval)"]:::promote
    DECIDE -->|Promote Sandbox/Perms| SEC["security-policy.md"]:::promote
    DECIDE -->|Defer| DEF["Defer<br/>(Wait for next signal)"]:::discard
    DECIDE -->|Discard| DISC["Discard<br/>(Retired, trail kept)"]:::discard

    HEUR --> SMARTER(["KB Grows<br/>Next session is smarter"]):::terminal
    PKB --> SMARTER
    CONST --> SMARTER
    SEC --> SMARTER

    SMARTER -.->|Smarter baseline| SESSION_END

    classDef terminal fill:#0d0d0d,stroke:#0d0d0d,color:#fff
    classDef sync fill:#10b981,stroke:#047857,color:#fff
    classDef triage fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#b45309,color:#fff
    classDef promote fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1d4ed8,color:#fff
    classDef discard fill:#fcf3f3,stroke:#f2c4c4,color:#c62828
    classDef decision fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#0d0d0d
